This collection allows you to upload an image of the author as well. To accomplish this, you will have to:

- Upload the image first & get the `id`

- Create the author record and pass the `id` to the `image` property on the author.


``` typescript
const uploadedImage = await uploadImageToApi(file);
const author = {
  // ... Rest of Author details
  image: uploadedImage.id
};

 ```

