item.description:
The endpoints here allows you to perform different actions on the `Review` collection type.

This collection allows you to add multiple images of the review as well. To accomplish this, you will have to:

- Upload the image(s) first & get the `id(s)`

- Create the review record and pass the `id(s)` to the `images` property on the review.


``` typescript
const uploadedImage = await uploadImageToApi(file);
const review = {
  // ... Rest of Review details
  images: [uploadedImage.id]
};

 ```
